</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-justify">接下来我们为Villa Maria设立非常详细的企业战略目标，并且把这个大目标具体细分到marketing goal和smart goals。另外，我们还为Villa Maria设定了公司整体的vision和mission。虽然看起来这两个概念非常空洞，但却是任何一份商业报告都不可或缺的部分，有时候正是这些空洞的口号才让我们的report看起来更加高大上。如果不知道report怎么写的同学们可以参考：report.lxws.net</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201019/390a7f7f5f5d4ab0b8cced799ee9eb83.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">PPT4是具体的目标市场和目标客户群定位。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201019/c7c33f6e6c874f1cab3d0c64e4f89926.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">接下来介绍一下Villa Maria的Marketing Mix模型，也就是市场营销中常用的4P（Product, Price, Place, Promotion）模型。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201019/6d2be71c200f473c9b2fec15c208e499.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">接下来就是大名鼎鼎的PEST分析体系了，我们分别从politics，economic，social和technological四个方面来对这个新西兰酒庄所处的外部宏观经济背景进行分析。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201019/a80e4e84e48b4a25ab2379d868536db3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">PEST 分析的结果。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201019/5bbd4662c6d949f78eda867f2507bb56.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">鉴于Villa Maria正打算大力在中国市场推广他们的产品，所以我们对中国的葡萄酒市场先做一个简单的介绍以便让读者能先大致了解一下市场情况。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201019/d047bab66cdf4a819d6090e125595837.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">接下来就是Villa Maria自身的竞争力分析，我们先用了波特五力分析模型（Five Forces Model）。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201019/ac26caab388a4de5accb3a20cad59c64.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">然后，再继续用SWOT模型来进一步剖析Villa Maria的优势和缺点。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201019/54efbf5373c34541bc4d58b9c2619cd3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">接下来，我们将会研究一下Villa Maria在中国市场上最大的竞争对手张裕葡萄酒公司。通过了解行业主要领导者的情况可以帮助Villa Maria更好的设计有针对性的营销推广计划。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201019/5418700b978645efad495cdf48f550e1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">PPT12对比了Villa Maria和张裕以及另外两个新西兰葡萄酒品牌在中国市场上的具体情况，包括经营年限，扩张速度，营收，产品质量等等因素。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201019/dd82d7c0cd9a4d788c0d6e75316330ff.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">PPT13我们分析了一下中国的葡萄酒市场并且基于这个市场的特点和未来的发展趋势给Villa Maria提出了一些营销推广上的意见。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201019/d70a3aca13264ddab91d7fc60cf70186.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">为了能更好的了解当地消费者的喜好，我们设计了一个简单的问卷调查，一共有5个核心的问题。通过这个方式可以帮助Villa Maria进一步了解市场的第一手信息。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201019/6ac8e1e4168e464dbe6c9cda1d6608c9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">问卷调查结果part 1</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201019/0d9d2e51634e432e84b5ac22f8733a37.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">问卷调查结果part 2</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201019/5f095718787a4ef38c6a5477a24e022b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">市场分析结果汇总</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201019/b310d63a2603448bb4fbbd213564fd6b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">基于上面的市场分析结果，我们得出的结论是Villa Maria的产品正处于一个相对成熟的阶段，虽然这个酒庄在中国市场的占有率较低，但却有着较为强劲的上升空间，我们建议Villa Maria采取market penetration strategy。通过开展一系列的市场推广活动可以帮助这家新西兰酒业公司快速打开市场。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201019/195935dcafb14cb5baba55d05ee57303.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">PPT19是我们预测的该酒庄2020-2022年这三年的目标营销额以及增长率。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201019/6b9c9132accc4987bac139928a805022.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">PPT20是一个大致的营销预算，主要分为5个分项目。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201019/88f7cecad6364d1bab4ec56aad03a757.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">PPT21是设计的一个监控计划用来实时监控营销计划的实施过程。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201019/8b965b04499a4e8384ae9f13325b2853.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">最后一张PPT我么设计了一个应变计划，具体从拓展新的销售渠道、推出针对中国消费者设计的产品包装、时刻追踪市场发展动向、和提高服务水平以达到增强品牌影响力这四方面展开。</p>
➜双语阅读 | 最全面的大学申请材料检查清单
http://www.sohu.com/a/425691498_490529	12603
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201019/f54008a5376e42f187725fa699cf99f0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>Transcripts</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>My transcripts meet university requirements</li>
</ul>
<p>For undergraduate applicants:</p>
<ul>
<li>4 years of Math</li>
<li>4 years of Primary Language</li>
<li>3-4 years of Science</li>
<li>3-4 years of Social Studies</li>
<li>6-10 advanced classes (honors, AP, IB, university-level)</li>
<li>My transcripts have been translated and verified, if required</li>
<li>I have submitted my transcripts</li>
<li>I have submitted my mid-year reports</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Demonstrated Interest</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>I have signed up to receive university email</li>
<li>I have “visited” each of the universities on my list by taking online tours or attending information sessions</li>
<li>I have contacted the admissions office, current students, and/or professors to learn more about each university</li>
<li>I have discussed why I am interested in attending each university in my corresponding personal statement, statement of purpose and/or supplemental essays</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Standardized Tests</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>I have submitted my standardized test scores to each university that requires them</li>
<li>I have submitted my standardized essay scores to each university that requires it</li>
<li>I have submitted my supplemental standardized test scores to each university that requires them</li>
<li>I have submitted my TOEFL or IELTS scores</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Letters of Recommendation (LOR)</strong></p>
<ul>
<li class="ql-align-justify">Each of my LORs include:</li>
<li>The background of my recommender</li>
<li>How my recommender knows me and for how long</li>
<li>Accurate, specific descriptions of my skills, abilities, accomplishments, and uniqueness</li>
<li>Concrete examples and/or anecdotes detailing my skills, abilities, accomplishments, and uniqueness</li>
<li>Information that compliments (rather than repeats) information in my other application materials</li>
<li>An offer to discuss my abilities and accomplishments over email or phone</li>
<li>A signed closing</li>
<li>Each of my recommenders has submitted their letters</li>
<li>I have given each of my recommenders a thank you note</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Primary Application Essay</strong></p>
<p><strong> &lt;a href="</strong>http://www.lxws.net/new.php?id=2393<strong>"&gt;Personal Statement&lt;/a&gt;</strong></p>
<ul>
<li class="ql-align-justify">I have fully answered the prompt</li>
<li class="ql-align-justify">I have started my personal statement with a captivating hook</li>
<li class="ql-align-justify">I have demonstrated my personal value(s)</li>
<li class="ql-align-justify">I have demonstrated my unique skills and qualities</li>
<li class="ql-align-justify">I have demonstrated motivation for advanced studies</li>
<li class="ql-align-justify">I have supported each of the claims I make about myself with evidence and examples</li>
<li class="ql-align-justify">My personal statement reads smoothly from start to finish</li>
<li class="ql-align-justify">I have proofread my essay</li>
<li class="ql-align-justify">The verb tense is the same throughout</li>
<li class="ql-align-justify">There are no fragments or run-on sentences</li>
<li class="ql-align-justify">All punctuation is correct</li>
<li class="ql-align-justify">Every word is spelled correctly</li>
<li class="ql-align-justify">I have had at least one other person read my essay for content, style, and grammar</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Statement of Purpose</strong></p>
<ul>
<li class="ql-align-justify">I have fully answered the prompt</li>
<li class="ql-align-justify">I have demonstrated knowledge of my discipline</li>
<li class="ql-align-justify">I have demonstrated motivation to pursue my discipline</li>
